## Acceptance Criteria

### Spinner
- [ ] Multiple preset animations available (dots, line, braille, moon, etc.)
- [ ] Animation advances on tick()
- [ ] Speed control works (ticks per frame)
- [ ] Label renders after spinner
- [ ] Wide character spinners (emoji) work correctly

### Progress Bar
- [ ] Ratio 0.0 renders empty bar
- [ ] Ratio 1.0 renders full bar
- [ ] Partial fill renders correctly
- [ ] Labels render at correct positions
- [ ] Multiple style presets available
- [ ] Works at any width

### ProgressWithEta
- [ ] ETA calculation is reasonable
- [ ] Items per second is accurate
- [ ] eta_string() formats nicely

### Integration
- [ ] Works in Agent Harness UI
- [ ] No flicker during animation
- [ ] Correct width handling

### Logging
- [ ] debug! on creation
- [ ] trace! on tick/render with state info

